description: Fueling your day with fantastic food, The Brunch Box is bringing an incredible menu to a curb near you! Whether you're looking for the most important meal of the day or a lovely lunch you're sure to love, then there's nobody better than this truck. Grab yourself an awesome Egg & Cheese Muffin, Sicilian Burger, Phat Philly Sandwich, or anything else of The Brunch Box's menu today!
name: The Brunch Box
